introduction: This video discusses the upcoming virtual conference on February 15th and 16th, featuring AI product owners, engineers, and keynote speakers such as Jason Louie, Shrea Shanar, and Tunji. The conference focuses on AI product development and engineering, with workshops covering topics like AI platform management and product management. The video also highlights the importance of evaluating AI models and their performance in production.

sections.title: Section 1: Introduction to the Virtual Conference
content: The virtual conference is coming up on February 15th and 16th.
It features AI product owners, engineers, and keynote speakers.
Some of the speakers include Jason Louie, Shrea Shanar, and Tunji.
The conference covers AI product development and engineering.

sections.title: Section 2: AI Product Owners and Engineers
content: The conference features AI product owners and engineers who work on developing AI products.
These professionals are responsible for ensuring that AI products meet the needs of their users and stakeholders.
They work closely with data scientists and other AI experts to design and implement AI solutions.
Some of the AI product owners and engineers featured in the conference include Jason Louie, Shrea Shanar, and Tunji.

sections.title: Section 3: AI Platform Management
content: The conference includes a workshop on AI platform management.
This workshop covers topics such as managing AI models and ensuring their performance in production.
Participants will learn how to evaluate the effectiveness of AI models and make improvements as needed.
The workshop is led by experts in the field of AI platform management.

sections.title: Section 4: AI Product Management
content: The conference also includes a workshop on AI product management.
This workshop covers topics such as product strategy, user experience, and product development.
Participants will learn how to develop AI products that meet the needs of their users and stakeholders.
The workshop is led by experts in the field of AI product management.

sections.title: Section 5: Evaluating AI Models
content: The conference highlights the importance of evaluating AI models in production.
Evaluating AI models helps ensure that they are providing accurate and reliable results.
Participants will learn how to set up evaluation frameworks and customize them for their specific needs.
The conference also discusses the challenges of evaluating AI models and how to overcome them.
